      • newMatchingDataConditional

        public static GenericTable.MatchingData newMatchingDataConditional(GenericTable.ContentFormatting contentFormatting,
                                                                   GenericTable.ContentAlignment contentAlignment,
                                                                   java.lang.String cellContentRegex,
                                                                   boolean conditional)
        Setup conditional matching
        Parameters:
        contentFormatting -
        contentAlignment -
        cellContentRegex -
        conditional - if
        true
        then only match contentAlignment and contentFormatting against the cell if cellContentRegex matches with the actual cell contents; this is necessary to determine non-emtpy cells
        false
        also match cellContentRegex against the cell (i.e. expect that all cells confirm to this pattern); this is the unconditional behavior from the ordinary constructor
        Returns:
        a new instance of this class
